            "abstractNote": "Summary\n            \n              1.\n               Here, I present a new, multifunctional phylogenetics package, phytools, for the R statistical computing environment.\n            \n            \n              2.\n               The focus of the package is on methods for phylogenetic comparative biology; however, it also includes tools for tree inference, phylogeny input/output, plotting, manipulation and several other tasks.\n            \n            \n              3.\n               I describe and tabulate the major methods implemented in phytools, and in addition provide some demonstration of its use in the form of two illustrative examples.\n            \n            \n              4.\n               Finally, I conclude by briefly describing an active web‐log that I use to document present and future developments for phytools. I also note other web resources for phylogenetics in the R computational environment.",
